{"tid":159660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警收炸彈恐嚇電郵　警告周六警署或有炸彈","createTime":"2017-03-17T07:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T08:47:23.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb7a3a01d4368a19cd4b9ebc364da6d661d2555","tid":159660,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/photo/bkn-20170317150246891-0317_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170317150907\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170317150246891-0317_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170317150907&h=8b62eee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方收到炸彈恐嚇，有網民自本周一起，連續4日向警方發出恐嚇電郵，昨日更指「可能星期六不知邊間警署會有炸彈」，警隊已通報全港軍裝巡邏小隊，提醒前線人員要加強留意，由於電郵來自美國及新加坡，警方已將案件交由網絡及科技罪案調查科跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方內部WhatsApp群組流傳，指「電台剛用電郵通知全世界話，有人在網上聲稱會係星期六於警署放炸彈，但冇明目標，已通知pscu(巡邏小隊)訓示人員，要多加留意可物品及可疑人。」東網正向警方查詢。"},{"pid":"356cfdd7c65db69e159bb51ce6c32dcbf4fed671","tid":159660,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"又自導自演"},{"pid":"6a60ca1cf41d4f312389f379e9f2841d4ba213f8","tid":159660,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"黃啟發"},{"pid":"0883406b73f87abfb944d39e3ba19d4cce15db5f","tid":159660,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"f2678cafe3f5043571b8ac3d89690bb48e507473","tid":159660,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"甘大滋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef527f650388b466873b3068891f55ec55d2881","tid":159660,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃啟發</blockquote><br />\n甘大滋呀！！"},{"pid":"e2594e2280fb2ffa70dd840153dc2cb6ec21953d","tid":159660,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB